      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            The limit from the left side as <m>t</m> gets close to <m>112</m>:  <me>\lim_{t \rightarrow 112^-} L(t) =</me>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            The limit from the right side as <m>t</m> gets close to 112: <me>\lim_{t \rightarrow 112^+} L(t) =</me>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            What is <m>L(112)</m>?
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
